{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_11_03",
  "title": "佐伯遙子 3話 未来へ一歩踏み出せるように",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――月ストのライブ当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―—On the Day of the Moon Tempest Live",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 1.2666666229
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "月ストのみんな\nいつも以上にパフォーマンスに力が入っているわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone in Moon Tempest\nis putting more effort into their performance than usual.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "特に琴乃は、今回のライブに想いを込めているはずです\nでも、麻奈への想いなら遙子さんだって負けてませんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Especially Kotono—she must be putting her feelings into this live.\nBut as for your feelings for Mana‚ Haruko-san‚ you're no less than her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.8666666229
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、昔一週間だけマネージャーになってくれた時も\nそうやって私を励ましてくれたわよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ even when you were manager for just one week in the past‚\nyou encouraged me like that‚ didn't you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}君や麻奈ちゃんのおかげで\n私は今、ここにいられる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks to you‚ {user}-kun‚ and Mana-chan‚\nI am here now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.8666666229
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "沢山励ましてもらった分、私も届けてくるわね\n聞いてくれるみんなに……そして、麻奈ちゃんに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll deliver as much encouragement as I've received.\nTo everyone listening… and to Mana-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.8333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12121.315574600005,
          "startTime": 41.9879821975
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 41.7
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 41.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "月ストのライブにゲストとして\n参加させてもらえるなんて、本当に嬉しいわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As a guest at the Moon Tempest live‚\nI'm truly happy to be able to participate.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "さっき琴乃ちゃんが伝えてくれたように\n今日は、私の大切なお友達のお誕生日なの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As Kotono-chan just said‚\ntoday is the birthday of my dear friend.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 57.7000009734
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "これから私が歌うのは\nその大切なお友達、長瀬麻奈ちゃんの曲……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The song I'm about to sing is\nby that dear friend‚ Mana Nagase…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "この曲は、麻奈ちゃんが夢に向かって頑張る人に向けて\n発表した応援ソングなの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a cheer song she released for everyone working hard\ntoward their dreams.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 72.8000009734
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "……そして、麻奈ちゃんの遺した曲の中で\n私が一番大好きな曲",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…And among the songs Mana-chan left behind‚\nthis is the one I love most.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.2495369563,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 79.8666676401
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "今日は、この曲を聴いた人が\n心のコンパスの示した未来へ、一歩踏み出せるように",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today‚ I hope everyone who hears this song\ncan take a step toward the future their heart's compass points to.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 93.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈ちゃんの想いも込めて歌います。聴いて下さい\n――『voyage』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll sing it with Mana-chan's feelings in it. Please listen.\n—“Voyage”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.7666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6533.332359900001,
          "startTime": 94.5333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 95.4666696746
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（麻奈。お前の誕生日に……偶然にも、同じ会場で……）\n（遙子さんがステージに立っているぞ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Mana. On your birthday… coincidentally‚ in the same venue…）\n（Haruko-san is standing on stage…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 104.4333363413
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（あの時にも負けない、光の海の中に……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（In a sea of light that doesn't lose to back then…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.4333363413,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 109.0000075856
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "（……麻奈ちゃん）\n（私は、あなたという星に向かって進んでいたわ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…Mana-chan）\n（I was moving toward the star that was you.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "（地図なんてなくて、時に迷って）\n（あなたみたいになろうとしていた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Without a map‚ often losing my way‚）\n（I was trying to become like you.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.2666702271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 122.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "（……でも、麻奈ちゃんは言ってくれたよね）\n（そのままの遙子ちゃんでいいって）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…But‚ you told me—）\n（\"It's okay to just be yourself‚ Haruko-chan.\"）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.5666692098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "（あの言葉のおかげで、私は私だけの心のコンパスを）\n（見つけることが出来たわ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Thanks to those words‚ I was able to find）\n（my own heart's compass.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.9000025432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 138.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 139.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "（ねぇ、麻奈ちゃん。私のステージ、観てくれてる？）\n（あの時と同じ場所で、私、歌ってるよ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Hey‚ Mana-chan. Are you watching my stage?）\n（In the same place as back then‚ I'm singing.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.5666687012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03-hrk017.m4a",
      "text": "（あなたが私に贈ってくれた）\n（世界でたった一つのプレゼントを）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（The gift you gave me—）\n（the one and only gift in the world.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.2999944051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 157.2000019907
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（お前のことだ、これを観たら得意げに言うんだろうな）\n（「ほら、私の親友は最高にかっこいいでしょ」って）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（It's about you. You'd probably say it proudly if you saw this.）\n（\"See‚ my best friend is the coolest‚ right?\"）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.4666610718,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（なぁ、麻奈――）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Hey‚ Mana—）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.633335324,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 168.633335324
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03-hrk018.m4a",
      "text": "（麻奈ちゃん――）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Mana-chan—）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.733335324,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
