    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 177.3333485921
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です\n遙子さんにしか出来ない、最高のステージでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work.\nIt was the best stage only you could give.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.0666819255,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 178.0333445231
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 183.4999724905
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03-hrk020.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうね、{user}君\n私の歌、麻奈ちゃんに届いたかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ {user}-kun.\nI wonder if my song reached Mana-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.0000152588,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "きっと……いや、絶対に届いていますよ\nもしかしたら、感動で顔ぐしゃぐしゃかもですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Surely… no‚ it definitely reached her.\nMaybe she's all teary and messy-faced from being moved.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 194.8000152588,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 198.9999806285
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "それに、聴いた人達も励まされたと思います\nこの歌が支えになる人も、きっといるんじゃないかと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I think everyone who heard it was encouraged too.\nI'm sure there are people who will be supported by this song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 203.7000152588,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 207.6666483124
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03-hrk021.m4a",
      "text": "私の歌で、誰かが……\nそうね、私も誰かを励ますことが出来たなら、嬉しいわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With my song‚ someone…\nYes‚ if I was able to encourage someone‚ I'd be happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 214.0000152588,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 220.6333200653
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03-hrk022.m4a",
      "text": "この歌って、不思議なの。麻奈ちゃんの歌は\n麻奈ちゃんにしか歌えないって思うのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This song is strange. I think only Mana-chan\ncould sing her songs…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 225.3959291764,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03-hrk023.m4a",
      "text": "『voyage』だけは、不思議としっくりきて……\n麻奈ちゃんの歌のはずなのに、どこか違う気がする……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But “Voyage” somehow feels just right…\nEven though it's supposed to be hers‚ it feels a bit different…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 233.9666819255,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 239.0666605194
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03-hrk024.m4a",
      "text": "なんて。何度も聴いてるから\n勝手にそう思っちゃうのかもしれないけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe it's because I've listened so many times.\nI might just be imagining it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 242.2333485921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、作り始める前に、麻奈が言ってましたよ\nこの曲は遙子さんにも歌ってもらうつもりだって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ before she even started making it‚ Mana said\nshe wanted you to sing this song too‚ Haruko-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 250.1333485921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 253.6333312551
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03-hrk025.m4a",
      "text": "っ……じゃあ、エールっていうだけじゃなくて……\n最初から、私が歌うことも考えて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Then‚ it's not just a cheer…\nFrom the beginning‚ she intended for me to sing it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 260.6333485921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 265.4333078582
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "……遙子さんさえ良かったら\nこれからもこの曲を、歌い継いでもらえませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…If it's alright with you‚ Haruko-san‚\ncould you continue singing this song from now on?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 267.7333445231,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈は、一緒にステージで遙子さんと歌える日を\n楽しみにしていましたし、きっと喜ぶと思うんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana was looking forward to the day she could sing with you on stage‚\nand I'm sure it would make her very happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 275.3000111897,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 279.966622881
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03-hrk026.m4a",
      "text": "っ……うん……分かった。麻奈ちゃんの分も\n私が沢山の人に届くように、歌わせてもらうわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes… I understand. For Mana-chan too‚\nI'll sing it so it can reach as many people as possible.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 288.3333445231,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_03-hrk027.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈ちゃんと……私の、この曲を",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This song… Mana-chan's and mine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 293.2665842253,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}